{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-classic\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-undefined=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B23%2C0%2C43%5D%2C%5B23%2C0%2C43%5D%5D%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><p data-lake-id=\"6cb4ef2b59a91797e7d11daa876f2e93\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">OneNote 2016 的搜索问题主要还是集中在页内搜索上。uwp 版解决了搜索 bug，然而 uwp 版的功能要弱得多。</p><p data-lake-id=\"ddcd162a05733d78f1b1ce184d677980\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"28376d42ba385510f324ae8371b6c357\" id=\"QtDTR\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">情形一：以数字或字母开头的行</h1><p data-lake-id=\"ffb3f7c0a1466dff9b26b6925c6550f4\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"54611e538038ba8a96f3ef3a2bce555a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">如果某一行以数字或字母开头，页内搜索这一行后面的字母、数字和中文，全部不会高亮。</p><p data-lake-id=\"1ecb1600d421a0975d7bfc672ca9e611\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"a3f8c8b42438f8a915767d7d97db2815\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">有一个通用解决方法是在被搜索的关键词前面加个逗号之类的符号，显然，这种方法没什么实用价值。</p><p data-lake-id=\"ed719326719433905c00179622dd43a0\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul data-lake-id=\"5817332498799e88246151cd5dfee1e6\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"e75294a2257f90fe8690e0a76ff2d4d0\">例子1：某行以 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">police_car</code> 开头，页内搜 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">car</code> 不会高亮，但是把开头改成 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">police car</code> 就可以高亮了</li><li data-lake-id=\"4e01570ac63f7d0a5702cca2b2266a7b\">例子2：某行以 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">police_警察</code> 开头，页内搜 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">警察</code> 不会高亮，但是把开头改成 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">police 警察</code> 就可以高亮了</li><li data-lake-id=\"0c4a64b61fa84ed0aed3d2371d72c2f6\"><span>例子3：某行开头的内容是 </span> <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">police car 出现了，说明警察来了</code>&nbsp;，搜 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">警察</code>&nbsp;不会高亮，但是加个冒号把内容改成 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\"><span>police car 出现了，说明：警察来了</span></code> 就可以高亮了</li><li data-lake-id=\"9c416d3760d0129a35be363ff8384ed9\">例子4：某行以 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">police_110</code> 开头，页内搜 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">110</code> 不会高亮，但是把开头改成 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">police 110</code> 就可以高亮了</li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"b7cb25748053482fe15fbdb94832b843\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"7ec034e46d2a7a1c555daadd2af7a860\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><strong><span>对于这种情形，最佳的通用解决方法是在搜索时用英文引号包裹搜索关键词</span></strong><span>，使用这种方法的前提是……该关键词必须由非 ASCII 字符组成（比如中日韩文字），英文单词和数字反而不行？</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"9d3519b8ce549d11200da8a4d9aa5e24\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span><br></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"dac609153bfcc0e1fc7d8b73d592279c\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">更奇葩的是，虽然以上的每一个例子都是我实际测试过的，但如果搜的是中文，并不能保证 100% 复现？</p><p data-lake-id=\"4ab9afd73aaf389f423fc3f7959e20a1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span><br></span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"14058900190c98eb1386a35a656b8528\" id=\"S7MTe\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">情形二：以字母开头的非标准词汇</h1><p data-lake-id=\"92f3c5e6e4c07a63c3d8ca3fa53c8e73\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"dadfc44e6b8a0d3217244a776a6a08d1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">对以字母开头的非标准词汇进行搜索，其它以同样字母开头的词汇统统会被高亮。</p><p data-lake-id=\"e6132230f4694bd7cbb89ff72aa4ac6c\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"8713d217ee2f82039519a7a5107536ba\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><strong>对于第二种情形，也可以在搜索时用英文引号包裹搜索关键词来解决</strong>。</p><p data-lake-id=\"50d4b6704df5610349f15b982cee4cf4\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul data-lake-id=\"1ff9c2f7758990dbd12f72de09842089\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"832a17f7a774abe882fe6ab3e2e238d0\">例子1： 文本为 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">想要c位出道就来参加xx营吧，You can you up，no can no bb！</code>，页内搜索 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">c位出道</code>，结果后面的 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">can</code>&nbsp;也被高亮了</li><li data-lake-id=\"ec1a8de30662318a2b13950aaa737ca4\">例子2：文本为 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">当时我po出了一张内涵照片，没想到别人没get到我的point</code>，页内搜索 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">po出</code>，后面的 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">point</code>&nbsp;也被高亮了</li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"db6de2c1010985d728f804d4938ab90f\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"8d8e74b662f2c6372f6c3d3acf2f7b97\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">（这些例子告诉我们，如果没有必要，那就尽量不要中英混用，不光人类会觉得你土，连软件都会嫌弃你 ）</p><p data-lake-id=\"846e71602b3f2b83b6861d814850a184\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"aaa27ed7facef54838b4ab849c2d09d1\" id=\"SstiU\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px;\">情形三：从外部复制的内容</h1><p data-lake-id=\"c180841f531908b9a48a850c8f95173a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"3fad7eab519b477b3475f0fc7855e29b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">其它玄学搜索 bug，主要出现在外部复制的文本上，特别是从网页复制进 OneNote 的文本。这种文本的搜索要么就一切正常，要么就出现各种千奇百怪的情况，比如同一段文字里某个词出现了 10 次，但只有 8 个被高亮，不被高亮的那两个上面根本找不出任何特征。而一旦出了问题，<strong>用英文引号包裹关键词根本不顶用</strong>。</p><p data-lake-id=\"ed68739ac093624ef9bf7b4ad8282fc7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ed9d5c25ab6b780776f8d2b532f76393\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">当出现不可分析的搜索 bug，可以靠 onetastic 插件的 Search Multi-Keywords marco 挽救一下。</p></div>",
